<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-q-and-a-what-to-eat-for-a-healthy-heart/">Mayo Clinic Q and A: What to eat for a healthy heart</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
